ket will be resolved based on the political party that wins the greatest number of seats in the Tamil Nadu Legislative Assembly in the 2026 election.\n\nIt is not about who forms the government, it is about who wins the maximum number of seats.\n\nTotal Constituencies in Tamil Nadu: 234\n\nSeats Contested:\n\nDMK – 164 seats\nADMK – 166 seats\nTVK – 233 seats\nNTK – 234 seats\nINC – 28 seats\nBJP – 26 seats\n\nWhoever wins the highest number of seats will be considered the winner in this context.\n\nExample:\nINC is in alliance with DMK. If INC wins 20 seats and DMK wins 70 seats, DMK’s total is 70.\n\nBJP is in alliance with ADMK. If BJP wins 15 seats and ADMK wins 50 seats, ADMK’s total is 50.\n\nIf TVK wins 71 seats, then TVK will be the winner here, even if it does not form the government.","parentEntityType":"Event","parentEntityID":119296,"userAddress":"0x67915f4d29ffb9ff1a007c4810fb5f15e9d61eee","createdAt":"2026-05-02T04:53:38.303618Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-02T04:53:47.896035Z","profile":{"name":"Honeybees","pseudonym":"Dearest-Lining","displayUsernamePublic":true,"bio":"","proxyWallet":"0x99ef735bd6a4943cd13f8784631f3fd4121eab48","baseAddress":"0x67915f4d29ffb9ff1a007c4810fb5f15e9d61eee","profileImage":"https://polymarket-upload.s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/profile-image-2871399-df038585-7919-4e4d-ac55-3c09364607f8.webp"},"reactions":[{"id":"2831095","commentID":2871972,"reactionType":"HEART","userAddress":"0xd833ffa68d4527103ceac3f6f488ddb1f51b3677","profile":{"proxyWallet":"0xbbf4d9f5078167e354937523c28dd4b4665d3b45"}},{"id":"2831195","commentID":2871972,"reactionType":"HEART","userAddress":"0xf568535c10d5b5479f18241e429bd9dd600c8be8","profile":{"proxyWallet":"0xa9677b1c9a9769bbcabc27c8d679b9f6ed33f0b4"}},{"id":"2831263","commentID":2871972,"reactionType":"HEART","userAddress":"0xc6632c019d63b2b6523fd8f6bad71ffa0a761847","profile":{"proxyWallet":"0x3748e88f10d7fe708a247daed43ea9453fec885e"}}],"reportCount":0,"reactionCount":3},{"id":"2871978","body":"Accordi